Name: Bishkek
Description: Bishkek (Бишкек) (population in 2009 approx. 835,000) is the capital and largest city in Kyrgyzstan.

Name: Balykchy
Description: Balykchy (Балыкчы) is a city at Issyk Kul.

Name: Karakol
Description: Karakol (Каракол) is a city in Kyrgyzstan on the east of Lake Issyk Kul.

Name: Kochkor
Description: Kochkor is a town in Kyrgyzstan's Issyk-Kul and the Tian Shan region.

Name: Osh
Description: Osh is a city in the Ferghana Valley of Kyrgyzstan.
